===Etymology===
From the [[Hawaiian]] [[pidgin]] word '''[[wiki]]''', from English '''[[quick]]''', plus English '''[[dictionary]]'''.

===Proper noun===
'''Wiktionary''' (''plural:'' '''[[Wiktionaries]]''')

# A [[collaborative]] project to produce a [[free]] and [[complete]] [[dictionary]] ([[lexicon]] and [[thesaurus]] therein) in every [[language]]. It is run by the [[Wikimedia Foundation]].
# A wiki-based, open-content dictionary.

shut up

